org.eclipse.e4.ui.model.application.ui

Enum SideValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SideValue>
      • org.eclipse.e4.ui.model.application.ui.SideValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SideValue>

    public enum SideValue
extends Enum<SideValue>
    A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Side Value', and utility methods for working with them.

    An enum providing the specific values determining the side of a trimmedWindow on which particular trim bars should be displayed.

    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    UiPackageImpl.getSideValue()
